{"tid":1686288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大波Man吹雞拆花壇變圍警署","createTime":"2019-11-01T04:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T05:00:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e33362e2dee5cb8a832f09f68a7f64a5b673d6b2","tid":1686288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:40:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191101/CUA4BCBK65KLWJJUQR4B4ZXCFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191101%2FCUA4BCBK65KLWJJUQR4B4ZXCFM%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvMyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=f24ab79b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191101%2FCUA4BCBK65KLWJJUQR4B4ZXCFM%2F&h=fdf71cda\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191101/CUA4BCBK65KLWJJUQR4B4ZXCFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n大波Man吹雞拆花壇變圍警署<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191101/large/1572542005_8f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191101%2Flarge%2F1572542005_8f68.jpg&h=a86fb757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人稱「大波Man」的石房有帶隊撐警，有大媽跟其合照。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有網友昨發起紀念太子站恐襲兩個月，藍絲親共群組近日亦密密吹雞，以千元報酬擬招募300人到太子站清理花壇，聲言行動獲警方合作。昨午太子站有百多人在「大波Man」率領下先到旺角警署撐警，但並沒清拆花壇，喊了幾句口號就散去。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：Green Object接管蘭桂坊 嘩鬼掃興<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫撐警口號後即四散<br />\n<br />\n藍絲親共群組近日不斷在互聯網及手機群組吹雞募集人手，有貼文甚至聲言每位參加者可獲現金1,000元作為報酬，內容大致是叫人到太子站花壇拆壇，並指另一批為數300人則負責做「花生友」，當清拆行動進行時，花生友負責吶喊助威，又謂會通知警方到場清場。<br />\n<br />\n昨下午近2時，著名藍絲人物、人稱「大波Man」的石房有，帶同逾百名大媽及阿叔現身旺角警署外，眾人圍着旺角警署外圍走，沿途高叫「警察加油」。其後一行人轉往太子站，但各人抵達後，叫了幾句口號後便後勁不繼，四散離開，沒有前往B1出口太子站花壇，其間亦未發生任何衝突。至於他們是否有接受1,000元報酬，則不得而知。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉漢權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/0S-zSFxvFCmqeD9lQEFMAEAWUmw=/802x506/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SACZ63MPFSTFR2RRIVVL2LALZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F0S-zSFxvFCmqeD9lQEFMAEAWUmw%3D%2F802x506%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSACZ63MPFSTFR2RRIVVL2LALZY.jpg&h=5fafde9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n百多名藍絲昨沿旺角警署外圍行走並叫警察加油口號即散去。<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"c75f6d0f6e8a50f8f9d77360149ae72487e85cdd","tid":1686288,"uid":36578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"咁就有錢收，幾爽"},{"pid":"41fa191b6d0a288951d0aa7d4a08167cc4d8da0c","tid":1686288,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75f6d0f6e8a50f8f9d77360149ae72487e85cdd","tid":1686288,"uid":36578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"咁就有錢收，幾爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1043ee4cee3e7daf400b2bcd8080b029ed47a25","tid":1686288,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:59:32.000Z","msg":"叫佢哋上返行人路,慢啲即噴胡椒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d951106c5f3a6a4a7a94f7d9020c81d40dadbdef","tid":1686288,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>喂石房有 你幾時先同黃洋達隻揪？</strong></span></span>"}]}